opencv camera actvity vs. view


activity 
- implements CvCameraViewListener2
- private CameraBridgeViewBase mOpenCvCameraView;
- Mat mRgba
- mOpenCvCameraView instantiate from xml
- mOpenCvCameraView.setCvCameraViewListener(this);

- onPause()
	- mOpenCvCameraView.disableView if not null

- onResume()
	- OpenCVLoader.initAsync(OpenCVLoader.OPENCV_VERSION_2_4_3, this, mLoaderCallback);

- onDestroy()
	-  	if (mOpenCvCameraView != null)
        	mOpenCvCameraView.disableView();

- void onCameraViewStarted(int width, int height)

- void onCameraViewStopped() 
	- release all matrices

- Mat onCameraFrame (CvCameraViewFrame inputFrame)


view funcs
- extends JavaCameraView implements PictureCallback
- void takePicture

- void onPicturrTaken(byte[] data, Camera camera)